{"id":18022,"date":"2022-12-31T04:25:37","date_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:25:37","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/nd.wv3.net\/amg-car\/bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong-co-dot-trong.html"},"modified":"2022-12-31T04:25:37","modified_gmt":"2022-12-31T04:25:37","slug":"bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong-co-dot-trong","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/2022\/12\/31\/bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong-co-dot-trong\/","title":{"rendered":"B\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee1ng xe hybrid c\u00f3 g\u00ec kh\u00e1c so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed1t trong?"},"content":{"rendered":"<\/p>\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\n<ul class=\"social_left\">\n<li>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"myvne_save_for_later\" data-token=\"32b9e1536f4864538ef313591b38052a\" data-article-id=\"4548290\" title=\"L\u01b0u b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft\">\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"li_comment\"><span class=\"number_cmt txt_num_comment num_cmt_detail\" data-type=\"comment\" data-objecttype=\"7\" data-objectid=\"4548290\"><\/span><\/li>\n<li><span class=\"tip\">Quay l\u1ea1i Xe h\u01a1i<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h1>B\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee1ng xe hybrid c\u00f3 g\u00ec kh\u00e1c so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed1t trong?<\/h1>\n<h2>C\u00e1c m\u1eabu xe hybrid c\u1ee7a Toyota c\u00f3 quy tr\u00ecnh b\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 xe \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed1t trong, v\u1edbi \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u, gi\u1ea3m kh\u00ed th\u1ea3i v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c l\u00e1i th\u00fa v\u1ecb. <\/h2>\n<p>Sau kho\u1ea3ng 2 n\u0103m b\u00e1n ch\u00ednh h\u00e3ng xe hybrid t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Toyota \u0111\u00e3 b\u00e0n giao 5.566 chi\u1ebfc \u0111\u1ebfn tay kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng Vi\u1ec7t, chi\u1ebfm kho\u1ea3ng 11% t\u1ed5ng doanh s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c m\u1eabu Corolla Cross, Camry v\u00e0 Corolla Altis.  Con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e3ng xe Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 11\/2022, kh\u00f4ng t\u00ednh c\u00e1c d\u00f2ng hybrid Toyota nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u kh\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh h\u00e3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. <\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong.jpg\" title=\"bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong.jpg 1100w\"><\/p>\n<p>Nh\u1eefng \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh khi\u1ebfn xe hybrid ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam, k\u00e9o theo vi\u1ec7c ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn chi ph\u00ed s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee1ng.  Ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed1t trong truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng, xe hybrid c\u00f3 th\u00eam kh\u1ed1i pin v\u00e0 m\u00f4-t\u01a1 \u0111i\u1ec7n, vi\u1ec7c s\u1ea1c \u0111i s\u1ea1c l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u1eddi gian b\u1ea3o h\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a kh\u1ed1i pin.  pin lai. <\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672431725_54_bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong.jpg\" title=\"1672431725_54_bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672431725_54_bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672431725_54_bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672431725_54_bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672431725_54_bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672431725_54_bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong.jpg 1100w\"><\/p>\n<p>\u201cNhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng lo ng\u1ea1i pin hybrid c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 pin \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i, nhanh xu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i s\u1ea1c \u0111i s\u1ea1c l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n n\u00ean kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec7n gi\u1ea3m\u201d, PGS.  TS \u0110\u00e0m Ho\u00e0ng Ph\u00fac, Tr\u01b0\u1edfng khoa K\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt \u00f4 t\u00f4, \u0110\u1ea1i h\u1ecdc B\u00e1ch khoa H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i cho bi\u1ebft.  \u201cVi\u1ec7c b\u1ed9 \u1eafc quy hybrid c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n s\u1ea1c ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng ri\u00eang, nh\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ednh to\u00e1n vi\u1ec7c s\u1ea1c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd c\u1ee7a \u1eafc quy, con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh xe. Do \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 khuy\u1ebfn c\u00e1o T\u1eeb nh\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t\u201d. <\/p>\n<p>B\u1ed9 pin tr\u00ean c\u00e1c m\u1eabu xe hybrid c\u1ee7a Toyota t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i Nickel-metal Hydride (NiMH) kh\u00e1 ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn trong ng\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nghi\u1ec7p \u00f4 t\u00f4.  \u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a lo\u1ea1i pin n\u00e0y l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec7t cao, ch\u1ed1ng ch\u00e1y n\u1ed5, s\u1ea1c nhanh v\u00e0 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd cao. <\/p>\n<p>Theo th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb Toyota Vi\u1ec7t Nam, c\u1ee5m pin hybrid tr\u00ean Camry 2.5HEV c\u00f3 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ecd t\u1eeb 15 \u0111\u1ebfn 20 n\u0103m, th\u1eddi gian b\u1ea3o h\u00e0nh l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 7 n\u0103m ho\u1eb7c 150.000 km t\u00f9y theo \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u01b0\u1edbc.  Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, h\u00e3ng khuy\u1ebfn c\u00e1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 l\u1ecbch b\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 xe \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed1t trong truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 n\u00ean ki\u1ec3m tra t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00fd \u1ee7y quy\u1ec1n 6 th\u00e1ng\/l\u1ea7n n\u1ebfu \u00edt s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"3-jpg-mobile-6256-1671024429\" alt=\"3-JPG-5097-1671024429.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/3-jpg-mobile-6256-1671024429.jpg\" data-desktop-src=\"https:\/\/amg.wv3.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672431725_138_Bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong.jpg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/3-jpg-mobile-6256-1671024429-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/3-jpg-mobile-6256-1671024429-600x399.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/3-jpg-mobile-6256-1671024429.jpg 640w\"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"4-jpg-mobile-1189-1671024429\" alt=\"4-JPG-8663-1671024429.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/4-jpg-mobile-1189-1671024429.jpg\" data-desktop-src=\"https:\/\/amg.wv3.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672431725_798_Bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong.jpg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/4-jpg-mobile-1189-1671024429-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/4-jpg-mobile-1189-1671024429-600x399.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/4-jpg-mobile-1189-1671024429.jpg 640w\"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"5-jpg-mobile-1394-1671024429\" alt=\"5-JPG-6955-1671024429.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/5-jpg-mobile-1394-1671024429.jpg\" data-desktop-src=\"https:\/\/amg.wv3.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672431726_285_Bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong.jpg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/5-jpg-mobile-1394-1671024429-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/5-jpg-mobile-1394-1671024429-600x399.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/5-jpg-mobile-1394-1671024429.jpg 640w\"><\/p>\n<p>T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1, vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee1ng xe hybrid kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi xe \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed1t trong truy\u1ec1n th\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a Toyota.  V\u00ed d\u1ee5 xe Camry 2.5HEV \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1y kho\u1ea3ng 1 v\u1ea1n km, b\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1edf m\u1ee9c trung b\u00ecnh th\u00ec xe c\u1ea7n thay nh\u1edbt m\u00e1y, l\u1ecdc nh\u1edbt, ph\u1edbt nh\u1edbt.  T\u1ed5ng chi ph\u00ed cho nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3n n\u00e0y v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 1,3 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng, kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c so v\u1edbi Camry \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed1t trong th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng. <\/p>\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u1ea5u tr\u00fac hybrid tr\u00ean c\u00e1c m\u1eabu xe c\u1ee7a Toyota kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n b\u1ea3o tr\u00ec, b\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u1ef3.  Chi ti\u1ebft duy nh\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u00f4 t\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed1t trong l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 l\u1ecdc gi\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m m\u00e1t h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng pin hybrid.  \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn gi\u00fap l\u00e0m m\u00e1t kh\u1ed1i pin trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng.  N\u1ebfu b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn n\u00e0y b\u1ecb t\u1eafc ho\u1eb7c b\u1ea9n, hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0m m\u00e1t c\u1ee7a pin hybrid s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3m, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ec7 truy\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a xe b\u1ecb h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf c\u00f4ng su\u1ea5t. <\/p>\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn n\u00e0y c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1, xe s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o l\u00ean m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh trung t\u00e2m ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e1i ki\u1ec3m tra, b\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee1ng.  Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 l\u1ecdc gi\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 hay l\u1ecdc gi\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00f2a, khi v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh xe trong \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, l\u1ecdc gi\u00f3 l\u00e0m m\u00e1t \u1eafc quy hybrid c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ec3m tra \u1edf m\u1ecdi c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee1ng. <\/p>\n<p>\u201cL\u1ecdc gi\u00f3 l\u00e0m m\u00e1t \u1eafc quy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt vi\u00ean ki\u1ec3m tra tr\u1ef1c quan sau m\u1ed7i 10.000 km, v\u1ec7 sinh sau m\u1ed7i 30.000 km trong \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng\u201d, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Toyota Vi\u1ec7t Nam cho bi\u1ebft.  \u201cL\u1ecdc gi\u00f3 n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 thay th\u1ebf khi c\u00f3 hi\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u00e1ch, kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh. Chi ph\u00ed thay th\u1ebf t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1edbi l\u1ecdc gi\u00f3 th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u00ean xe\u201d. <\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"6-jpg-mobile-5279-1671024429\" alt=\"6-JPG-8294-1671024429.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/6-jpg-mobile-5279-1671024429.jpg\" data-desktop-src=\"https:\/\/amg.wv3.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672431726_762_Bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong.jpg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/6-jpg-mobile-5279-1671024429-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/6-jpg-mobile-5279-1671024429-600x399.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/6-jpg-mobile-5279-1671024429.jpg 640w\"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"7-jpg-mobile-2567-1671024429\" alt=\"7-JPG-1827-1671024429.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/7-jpg-mobile-2567-1671024429.jpg\" data-desktop-src=\"https:\/\/amg.wv3.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672431726_583_Bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong.jpg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/7-jpg-mobile-2567-1671024429-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/7-jpg-mobile-2567-1671024429-600x399.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/7-jpg-mobile-2567-1671024429.jpg 640w\"><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img_pc\" title=\"8-jpg-mobile-7431-1671024429\" alt=\"8-JPG-1488-1671024429.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/8-jpg-mobile-7431-1671024429.jpg\" data-desktop-src=\"https:\/\/amg.wv3.net\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672431726_204_Bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong.jpg\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/8-jpg-mobile-7431-1671024429-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/8-jpg-mobile-7431-1671024429-600x399.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/8-jpg-mobile-7431-1671024429.jpg 640w\"><\/p>\n<p>    Ngo\u00e0i ra, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng Toyota hybrid c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u00e3ng khuy\u1ebfn c\u00e1o n\u00ean theo d\u00f5i m\u1ee9c n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0m m\u00e1t cho b\u1ed9 bi\u1ebfn t\u1ea7n (HV Inverter) trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng, m\u1ee9c l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng l\u00e0 gi\u1eefa d\u00f2ng Low v\u00e0 Full.  Vi\u1ec7c thi\u1ebfu n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0m m\u00e1t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn xe hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o l\u1ed7i tr\u00ean m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh.  C\u1ea5u t\u1ea1o xe Toyota hybrid v\u1eabn s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng b\u00ecnh \u1eafc quy 12V song song v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 \u1eafc quy hybrid, n\u1ebfu b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn n\u00e0y y\u1ebfu ho\u1eb7c c\u1ea1n ki\u1ec7t h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111i\u1ec7n s\u1ebd ng\u1eebng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng. <\/p>\n<p>\u201cGi\u1ed1ng xe \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed1t trong, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng Toyota hybrid c\u1ea7n ch\u00fa \u00fd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng phanh v\u00e0 v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 P khi \u0111\u1ed7 xe. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 m\u00f4-t\u01a1 \u0111i\u1ec7n, m\u00e1y ph\u00e1t \u0111i\u1ec7n v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng hybrid tr\u00ean xe\u201d, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n n\u00e0y n\u00f3i.  \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Toyota Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0a ra khuy\u1ebfn ngh\u1ecb.<\/p>\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1ec1 chi ph\u00ed b\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee1ng, xe hybrid c\u1ee7a Toyota ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u.  C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Camry 2.5HEV c\u00f3 m\u1ee9c ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u ch\u1ec9 4,4 l\u00edt\/100km, con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y \u1edf Camry 2.5Q \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed1t trong l\u00e0 7,09 l\u00edt\/100 km.  M\u1ee9c ti\u00eau th\u1ee5 nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n khi\u1ebfn xe hybrid c\u1ee7a Toyota c\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00ed th\u1ea3i CO2 \u00edt h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi xe c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng dung t\u00edch \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1. <\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672431726_767_bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong.jpg\" title=\"1672431726_767_bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672431726_767_bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672431726_767_bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672431726_767_bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672431726_767_bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672431726_767_bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong.jpg 1100w\"><\/p>\n<p>Toyota Camry 2022 t\u1ea1i Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadp kh\u1ea9u nguy\u00ean chi\u1ebfc t\u1eeb Th\u00e1i Lan v\u1edbi 4 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n: 2.0G, 2.0Q, 2.5Q v\u00e0 2.5HV, gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t: 1,05 t\u1ef7, 1,167 t\u1ef7, 1,349 t\u1ef7 v\u00e0 1,441 t\u1ef7 (\u0111\u00e3 bao g\u1ed3m VAT). <\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672431727_894_bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong.jpg\" alt=\"B\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee1ng xe hybrid v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed1t trong kh\u00e1c nhau\" title=\"1672431727_894_bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong\" srcset=\"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672431727_894_bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672431727_894_bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong-600x360.jpg 600w, https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/12\/1672431727_894_bao-duong-xe-hybrid-co-gi-khac-so-voi-dong.jpg 750w\"><\/p>\n<p>B\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee1ng xe hybrid v\u1edbi c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed1t trong N\u1ed9i dung: Tu\u1ea5n V\u0169 \u2013 \u1ea2nh v\u00e0 Video: Toyota Vi\u1ec7t Nam<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align:right\"><strong>AMGCAR.VN<\/strong><\/p>\n<\/p><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Quay l\u1ea1i Xe h\u01a1i B\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee1ng xe hybrid c\u00f3 g\u00ec kh\u00e1c so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed1t trong? C\u00e1c m\u1eabu xe hybrid c\u1ee7a Toyota c\u00f3 quy tr\u00ecnh b\u1ea3o d\u01b0\u1ee1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 xe \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed1t trong, v\u1edbi \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m nhi\u00ean li\u1ec7u, gi\u1ea3m kh\u00ed th\u1ea3i v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c l\u00e1i th\u00fa v\u1ecb. Sau kho\u1ea3ng 2 [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":16835,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[75],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/18022"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=18022"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/18022\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/16835"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=18022"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=18022"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/amgcar.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=18022"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}